// BP_LightShard — Blueprint subclass of ALightShardPuzzleActor
// Location: /Game/Game/Blueprints/Actors/BP_LightShard

/*
To create in UE5 Editor:
1. Create new Blueprint class extending ALightShardPuzzleActor
2. Set default properties:
   - PuzzleName = "Light Shard Alpha"
   - RequiredRole = Light
   - LightIntensity = 5000
   - LightRadius = 800
   - LightColor = FLinearColor(1.0, 0.85, 0.4)
   - ActiveMaterial = M_LightShard_Active (golden glow)
   - InactiveMaterial = M_LightShard_Inactive (dim)
   - ActivationSound = S_LightShard_Activate_Cue
   - MeshComp → StaticMesh = SM_Shard_Crystal
3. Place 3x instances in PrototypeRoom at:
   - (-400, 0, 100)
   - (-200, 300, 100)
   - (0, 600, 100)
*/
